\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'93Idomeneus,\uc0\u8232 may the man who will not fight today,\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0270\u8232 and willingly, never return from Troy.\u8232 May he become a toy for dogs to play with.\u8232 But get your armour and then come with me.\u8232 If we\'92re to work well, we must work together,\u8232 although we\'92re only two. For courage\u8232 of the highest sort comes when men combine,\u8232 even among men worth very little,\u8232 and we two know how to battle with the best.\'94\
