\'93In my hut, too, and in my black ship,\uc0\u8232 there\'92s lots of Trojan loot. But it\'92s not close\'97\u8232 too inconvenient. For I can claim\u8232 I don\'92t neglect my fighting prowess.\u8232 Whenever battles start, I stand and fight\u8232 with men in front, in those encounters\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0[270]\u8232 where men win glory. Other Achaeans\u8232 might not know my fighting quality, but you,\u8232 I think you\'92ve seen it for yourself.\'94\
