\'93I know your courage. Why talk that way?\uc0\u8232 If by the ships right now we were naming\u8232 the best men for an ambush, where one sees\u8232 a warrior\'92s courage most conspicuously,\u8232 where cowards and brave men truly show themselves\'97\u8232 for a coward\'92s colour always changes,\u8232 the man\'92s so nervous he just can\'92t sit still,\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0[280]\u8232 shifting around, resting first on one foot,\u8232 then another, heart pounding in his chest,\u8232 his mind preoccupied with thoughts of death,\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0330\u8232 and his teeth keep chattering in his mouth,\u8232 while a brave man\'92s colour never changes,\u8232 he feels no great fear as he takes his place\u8232 in the group selected for the ambush,\u8232 no\'97he prays the killing will soon start.\u8232 In such a scene no one could challenge you,\u8232 or fault your battle rage or your strong arms.\u8232 For if, in the middle of the fighting,\u8232 some flying weapon hit you, or you were stabbed,\u8232 that weapon wouldn\'92t strike your neck or body\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0340\u8232 in the back. No, you\'92d be hit in front,\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0[290]\u8232 in chest or stomach, as you charged ahead,\u8232 getting your joy from fighting at the front.\u8232 But let\'92s not chat about this any longer,\u8232 standing here as if we were young children.\u8232 That could make some people very angry.\u8232 Go in my hut. Get yourself a heavy spear.\'94\
